Doc Spatz, don't tell it like it was.  Tell US like you FELT it!  This whole site is about impressions, feelings and thoughts.  I do not ask for a political dissertation or an excuse.  I am asking for your honest FEELINGS!  We here have all expressed our feelings for being who and what we are.  We are asking no less of you.  I told you a long time ago that I respected you as an individual but would not accept your political beliefs.  I am not asking for a spewing of your ideas but a vision through your eyes of the time and circumstances that brought you to the conclusion that the war was wrong.  I ask this for my understanding of the folks who are different from me today in their views and beliefs.  Looking forward to your posts.<br>

